               <p>"after having read in the newspapers an</p>
               <p>"account of the robbery at Mr. Gearing's</p>
               <p>"(which he did not know was the prisoner's</p>
               <p>"master) he had some conversation with the</p>
               <p>"prisoner respecting it, and the prisoner seemed</p>
               <p>"to have heard nothing of such a robbery."</p>
