               <p>"of town at the time Mr. Gearing's house was</p>
               <p>"robbed; that when he came to town he found<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177402160052"></xptr> " his chamber door broke open, and he missed</p>
               <p>"many things as mentioned in the indictment.</p>
               <p>"He deposed that the four table spoons produced</p>
