               <p>"house and a bed chamber at Mr. Gearing's;</p>
               <p>"that they were broke open, and he</p>
               <p>"missed the things mentioned in the indictment." This witness produced some shirts , which he deposed were his property; his mark was partly taken out of them, and in its stead, the name 
