               <p>"Gearing's house; that Hayward carried</p>
               <p>"away the plate from Mr. Gearing's; that they</p>
               <p>"gave one Hurley, who was capitally convicted</p>
               <p>"some few sessions ago, a guinea to find</p>
               <p>"out a Jew who would buy the plate. He said</p>
               <p>"he believed Mr. Bennet heard the prisoner's</p>
